      "abstract": "The BAI is a 21-item self-report measure assessing the severity of anxiety symptoms in adolescents and adults. Items describe anxiety symptoms and are rated on a 4-point scale (0=Not at all, 3=Severely). The BAI is useful for screening anxiety disorders and monitoring treatment response.",
